{
  "stem": "9701.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I was told now that I see that food is plentiful, I will want everything, and that's not healthy for me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, I need to increase my food intake gradually.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I stayed with the Rose family for 10 weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the entire 10 weeks, my diet consisted of a piece of toast, one piece of toast, and butter, and a cup of tea for breakfast, two pieces of toast and a cup of tea for lunch, and two more pieces of toast and tea for dinner.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On Sunday mornings, in addition to my one piece of toast and a cup of tea for breakfast, I also got a cookie.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was perhaps because Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rose, on Sunday mornings, served tea and cookies to everyone in the family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I shared a room with the middle daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since he brought her tea and a cookie, I guess he felt he ought to give me tea and a cookie also.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But two weeks before school was out, and school was out the end of July, I got a phone call from Beatrice Mayer, who had left with her family and her mother for France two days after I arrived in England, where they normally spent their summer.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But because it looked like a war might break out, they came back earlier.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so she called me to find out how I am.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was about 4:30 in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, how are you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for the first time, I was honest.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said, well, when are you going to eat dinner?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, well, it won't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so, she said, well, why-- and she sensed that something was wrong.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
